summary:

Anya, runs to Nat: Mama! I missed you...
body:
Natasha, goes in to the penthouse and sees Anya and Tony waiting for her: Baby! I’m home!

Anya, runs to Nat: Mama! I missed you so much!

Natasha, kneels and hugs Anya: I missed you, too! Were you a good girl?

Anya, nods: Yes!

Tony, crosses his arms to his chest: A bit.

Natasha, looks at Tony, questioning: A bit? Why? What happened?

Tony, sighs: I was called to her school. She had a fight with her classmate.

Natasha, eyebrows furrowed: Anastasia?

Anya, pouts: Because I said Spider-Man is my brother and she said I was lying…

Tony and Natasha, looking at each other:

Anya, tugs at their shirts: Peter is Spider-Man, right?
